# Crear servicios

Example: [pedido.service.ts](mdc:src/app/modules/operaciones/pedido/pedido.service.ts)
Additional Examples: 
- [pedido-item-sucursal.service.ts](mdc:src/app/modules/operaciones/pedido/pedido-item-sucursal/pedido-item-sucursal.service.ts)

Resources: 
- [generic-crud.service.ts](mdc:src/app/generics/generic-crud.service.ts)
- [main.service.ts](mdc:src/app/main.service.ts)

- you will create a service based on the examples
- always use [generic-crud.service.ts](mdc:src/app/generics/generic-crud.service.ts) for apollo querys and mutations: this.genericService.onGetById(this.getPedidoPorId, id); where this.getPedidoPorId is the graphql query service
- create all functions for each query and mutation that is located on /actual-path/graphql/
- add a small documentation in spanish for each method
- the service file name is always <service-name>.service.ts
- inject genericService and use its methods instead of implementing direct GraphQL calls
- include proper error handling through GenericCrudService
- follow the naming convention: onGet*, onSave*, onDelete*, etc.

